function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	idGulyasClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idGulyas, true)
	idAnetaClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(idAnetaStand, true)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGulyasClone) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idGulyasClone, idGulyasWalkloc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idGulyasClone, 1)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAnetaClone) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(idAnetaClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAnetaClone, idGulyasWalkloc, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idAnetaClone, 1)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(7)
	Hydra.EventSend("VeraArrives", idSelf)
	
end
